step-1:- Add Water, Sugar, Tea Leaves, Ginger, Tulsi in the utensil & boil the water.
step-2:-Now add the sufficient amount of Milk in the utensil.
step-3:- Now wait for 5 minutes or untill the colour of the tea will become dark brown.
step-4:- Now strain the Tea in the cup with the help of Strainer & Enjoy the cup of tea.